{
  "stem": "4032.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I do know that my sister and my younger brother went to the Chelmno, to the camp to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing during the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no-- no-- no correspondence, because when we were in Palestine in 1942, '43, there were not much coming news out of-- of course, we knew the general news that they are-- what they're doing to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't know exactly what, individually, they did to my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know that my older brother survived in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the liberation, he died after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My younger brother survived also through-- told me, one day, a story that they took him in the ovens, in the crematorium, and everybody between them, they said, if you open your shoelaces and you open all your this-- shirt, and-- the gas will kill you faster.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that moment, a sound was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and they said that the Red Cross came to visit that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they took everybody out of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was my brother, how he survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went about three-- two brothers, and one girl and I-- four of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From Warsaw to Siemiatycze, a town by the River Bug, which was the dividing line between Russia and-- Germany and Russia, occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to Warsaw wasn't too bad to travel, because trains were still going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went with a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Warsaw to Siemiatycze, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] horses, buggies, and all kind of-- I don't exactly remember how far it was, but we came at night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the borders were watched by-- on one side by the Germans, on one side by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
